CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1945, pg. 13 reads: "Beauty And... For high scholarship, leadership, and service, Louise W. Johnson was named to four University of Pittsburgh honor organizations recently, and was elected president of the Mortar Board. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Full length portrait of Louise W. Johnson, wearing striped top with wrap skirt, holding books and standing beside Cathedral of Learning, University of Pittsburgh, Oakland
